         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Most ¶  ¶ esteemed Professor, ¶  ¶ Enclosed you will ¶  ¶ receive ¶  ¶ the continuation of the Plantae ¶  ¶ Muellerianae, the ¶  ¶ Algae and Characeae. The remaining part of the cryptogams just needs ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">M53.12.07</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">From<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Wilhelm Sonder to<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Diederich von Schlechtendal</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS not seen; extracted from Tkach, Neubauer &amp; Roser (2022), Brief 18.</p>
               </note>Geehrtester Herr<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Professor!<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Anbei erhalten Sie die Fortsetzung der Plant. Müllerianae, die Algen und Characeen. Den übrigen Theil der Kryptogamen muss<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>ich nur noch abschreiben; in 8–14 Tagen soll er nachfolgen. Eine erste im Juni angekommene Nachsendung an Algen hat mich etwas länger aufgehalten als ich erwartete.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Wollen Sie die Güte haben und 25 Separatabdrucke davon abziehen lassen.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Der Druck der Phanerogamen wird auch bald weiter gehen können, da ich die Orchideen von Lindley zurückerhalten u einen anderen Theil selbst<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>bestimmt habe.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Wenn es Ihnen pass</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">t, wäre es mir</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>M</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">ü</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">ller’s wegen lieb, wenn die Sachen bald zum Drucke gelangen könnten, da er etwas ungeduldig ist und da die Hinsendung</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>nach Australien so viele Zeit erfordert. Da</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">ss</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Dr. M</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">ü</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">ller zum Colonial Botanist für die Provinz Victoria von dem die Botanik liebenden und beschützenden Gouverneur Latrobe ernannt ist, werde ich Ihnen schon in meinem vorigen Briefe mitgetheilt haben. Müller will gerne einige Exemplare von R. Brown’s</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Prodromus haben, ich<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">wei</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">ss aber wirklich nicht, wie ich ihm dieselben verschaffen soll.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Von den Müller’schen Sämereien ist viel aufgelaufen; ich selbst habe noch gegenwärtig mehrere niedliche Compositae, Pteropogon ramosissimus, Helipterum corymbiflor. etc. in Blüthe. Ich denke, Müller wird unsere Gärten jetzt erst recht bereichern, da er an die dortige Regierung nur die Reiseberichte und ein Exemplar für das Herbarium abzuliefern hat.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Hochachtungsvoll</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ihr<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>ergebener<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>W. Sonder</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Hamburg</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>d. 7 Decb. 1853</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Most<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>esteemed Professor,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Enclosed you will<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>receive<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the continuation of the Plantae<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Muellerianae, the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Algae and Characeae. The remaining part of the cryptogams just needs to be transcribed; it should follow in 8-14 days. A<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>transmission<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>of<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Algae<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>that<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>only<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>arrived in June has kept me somewhat<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>longer than I expected.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Would you be so kind as to have 25 separate<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>reprints of it struck off.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The printing of the phanerogams will also be able to continue soon, as I have received the orchids back from Lindley and have determined another part myself.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>If it suits you, I would appreciate it for Mueller's sake if the things could be printed soon, as he is somewhat impatient and as sending them to Australia takes so much time.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I have already informed you in my previous letter that Dr Mueller has been appointed Colonial Botanist for the Province of Victoria by Governor Latrobe, who loves and patronizes<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>botany. Mueller would like to have some copies of R. Brown's<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Prodromus</seg>, but I really do not know how<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I am<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>to get them for him.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>A lot of Mueller's seeds have come up; I myself still have several<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>lovely<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Compositae,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Pteropogon ramosissimus</seg>,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Helipterum corymbiflor</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">um</seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>etc in flower. I think Mueller will now enrich our gardens even more, as he only has to deliver the travel reports and one specimen for the herbarium to the government there.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Respectfully,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>devoted</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>W. Sonder</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Hamburg</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">7 December 1853</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
         </div>
      </body>
